@startuml Sequence Diagrams
!theme plain
autonumber

title Generación de JWT y Ciclo Tarea

actor "Estudiante" as S
participant "Frontend (App Router)" as F
participant "Auth Middleware" as MW
participant "FastAPI Router" as R
participant "Task UseCase" as UC
participant "EventBus" as EB
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Google Calendar API\n(Fase 7 - Stub)" as GCal

== 1. Autenticación ==
S -> F: Ingresa credenciales /login
F -> R: POST /api/v1/auth/login
R -> DB: Verifica Hash de Password
DB --> R: User Encontrado
R -> R: Genera JWT (HMAC-SHA256)
R --> F: Retorna JWT (Session)
F -> F: Guarda en Context local
F --> S: Redirige a /dashboard

== 2. Operación Acreditada: Completar Tarea ==
S -> F: Drag & Drop Tarea a "DONE"
F -> MW: PATCH /api/v1/tasks/{id}/status \nHeader: Bearer JWT
MW -> MW: Valida Signature y Expy
MW -> R: Request Autorizado
R -> UC: execute(user_id, task_id, "DONE")
UC -> DB: Fetch TaskDomain
DB --> UC: Task en "TODO"
UC -> UC: Estado válido -> change_status()
UC -> DB: Persiste Estado "DONE"
UC -> EB: publish(TaskCompletedEvent)
EB -> DB: Activa NotificationListener asíncronamente
EB -> GCal: (Stub Fase 7) Marcar Tarea Externa como Completada
R --> F: 200 OK actualiza caché
F --> S: UI muestra Tarea Completada

@enduml
